  • Konstruktordetails

    • FileBackup

      public FileBackup(String indentifier, File[] filesToBackup, File destinationPathToBackupToo, File rootDirectory)
      Creates a FileBackup instance with the specified parameters.
      Parameter:
      indentifier - Unique identifier for the backup.
      filesToBackup - Array of files to be backed up.
      destinationPathToBackupToo - The directory where backups will be stored.
      rootDirectory - The root directory where files will be searched for regex and unzipped after backup.

    • FileBackup

      public FileBackup(String identifier, List<RegexFileFilter> fileFilters, List<RegexFileFilter> excludeFilters, File destinationPathToBackupToo, File rootDirectory)
      Creates a FileBackup instance with the specified parameters.
      Parameter:
      identifier - Unique identifier for the backup.
      fileFilters - List of RegexFileFilter to include files in the backup.
      excludeFilters - List of RegexFileFilter to exclude files from the backup.
      destinationPathToBackupToo - The directory where backups will be stored.
      rootDirectory - The root directory where files will be searched for regex and unzipped after backup.
